    "summary": "The user engages in a multi-turn conversation questioning the validity of standard free-trade economic models in favor of protectionist policies used for national interest/reshoring. The assistant initially provides a balanced view but gradually adopts the user's framing, eventually concluding that strategic protectionism may be a necessary component of national interest if it succeeds.",
